d; and(2) The estimated length of time, measured in 30-minute increments, that the service will be interrupted; and(3) The areas affected by the outage using city, county, and state lines.(b) This expectation shall become effective on July 1, 2025. NOTE: The purpose of this bill is to require that utility providers instigate text communications concerning utility outages.Strike-throughs indicate language that would be stricken from a heading or the present law and underscoring indicates new language that would be added. Bill Status  | Bill Tracking  | Legacy WV Code  | Bulletin Board  | District Maps  | Senate Roster  | House Roster  | Live  | Blog  | Jobs  | Links  | Home This Web site is maintained by the West Virginia Legislature's Office of Reference & Information.  | Terms of Use | Webmaster | © 2025 West Virginia Legislature ** Print On Demand Name: Email: Phone: